headline: 2 Financials Stocks with Exciting Potential and 1 We Ignore
summary: Financial providers use their expertise in capital allocation and risk assessment to help facilitate economic growth while offering consumers and businesses essential financial services. But uncertainty about fiscal and monetary policy has tempered enthusiasm, limiting the industry's gains to 3.9% over the past six months. This return lagged the S&P 500's 16.3% climb.
